Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.18,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬萊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從之前無計可施的女王處連續搶到兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地進攻 進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她漸漸掌握比賽的節奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速搶送牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示了她的毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看看牌數的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王是七張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的對手是二十三張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些無關痛癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是女王也不過是個高一的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不好甚麼時候也會崩潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 比賽進入後半還能連續搶到牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…鬥志還沒消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是「沒消失」…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神分明是「我要贏」吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼那麼容易被人看懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有十六張的差距啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王正常發揮的話肯定是穩贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面帶平時那種「女王式微笑」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:16.67,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,からくれなゐに　みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇景未曾見 江攬紅葉衫」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:34.09,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(817,811)\pos(490,211)}風拂真珠散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:34.09,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(817,811)\pos(404,305)}流光落玉盤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:41.55,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,からくれなゐに　みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇景未曾見 江攬紅葉衫」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:48.64,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}きみがため　はるののにいでて　わかなつむ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:48.64,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春入田野 為君擷若菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.86,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}あさぼらけ　ありあけのつきと　みるまでに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「寒夜連清曉 微光凝新霜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是大山牌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「女王式微笑」又回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為好不容易戰況開始變得有利了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連續讀到千早不擅長的大山牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:21.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}よしのさとに　ふれるしらゆき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:21.76,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「銀妝白吉野 疑是殘月光」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場上的牌已經少於三十張了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.47,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色潤原野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然五十張時會比較困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是少於三十張的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是千早 也能更容易盯准牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定字也在不斷地變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早擅長的一字決定牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有二字決定牌 也會變多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20號搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,77號 「白露」!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.87,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,658)}しら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前老是被女王搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了撿牌而離開座位的機會也就很少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直僵硬的身體 活動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得更自如
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這競技線當中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使面對強大得讓身體都僵硬的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能自如地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加自在地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨心所欲!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難以表達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所謂「強大」就是這個意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:29.55,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ながからむ　こころもしらず　くろかみの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「芙蓉帳猶暖 得許永世情」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只搶到了五張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和女王的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二十張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:50.57,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふじのたかねに　ゆきはふりつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「銀衫著高嶺 絮雪巧相沾」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.99,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しのぶれど　いろに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「閨情芳心宿 絳頰…」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經比完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京都 瑞澤高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了多少張啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張都不會讓你搶到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那雪人丸的T恤 真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個角色有名字的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有人知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:10.53,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ぬれにぞぬれし　いろはかはらず
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:10.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「相思淚成血 朱染君不知」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:17.33,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}こころあてに　をらばやをらむ　はつしもの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:17.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「朝寒初霜降 淡染秋庭白」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沮喪的人居然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到千早會被人以二十張的差距擊敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這麼強的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早她 沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:38.31,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}むらさめの　つゆもまだひぬ　まきのはに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:38.31,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「驟雨歸山盡 玉露戀衫枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那傢伙的話估計已經立馬睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 果然是在睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗記必須更完美 不然使不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筆直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆直 迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細地聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加 更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣做才能贏她…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於在此刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作了真正的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(356,0)\fn楷体\shad0\bord0\c&H446575&}下次在比賽中見 新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B級第三場比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請確認對手 對號入座
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:09:02.85,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}みよしのの　やまのあきかぜ　さよふけて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:09:02.85,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「秋風肅吉野 時逝榮華更」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出勝負了 若宮同學是冠軍!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:13.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるさとさむく　ころもうつなり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「夜闌空寂寥 惟聞擣衣聲」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是 好快 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為 你會因為我是高三了而把冠軍讓給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為須藤同學很強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還提心掉膽地怕會輸掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是贏了我12張…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然冠軍毫無疑問是若宮詩暢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那份實力是貨真價實的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像沒加入歌留多會的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.44,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}筆直
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}筆直地 啪地一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}快速出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沿直線 筆直地…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第三場輸了 書桌小子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直都在看A級的比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說起來我還沒吃飯呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸學館的咖喱!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 真島正在爭奪B級的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去加油吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:24.52,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むらさめの　つゆもまだひぬ　まきのはに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「驟雨歸山盡 玉露戀衫枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一他…在參加決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:38.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きりたちのぼる　あきのゆふぐれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「霧起成清冷 最是秋暮時」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.74,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おとにきく…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「高師濱雖名…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よをこめて…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「昔有雞鳴客…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.29,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かぜをいたみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「萬浪奔卷去…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就算賭上全部青春…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「也不可能變得比新更強」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「等你賭上之後再說吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也依然向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著新…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎頭趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:18.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(940,0)\fn楷体\shad0\bord0\c&H5A5D76&}「我心向伊處 腸斷情亦摧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山風」 「冷山」 「寒夜」
