Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.49,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,658)}もろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.49,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(805,658)}つき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「晴春」「久別」「木津」「守卒」「陸奧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,658)}ひさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,658)}ひとは
